<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>CV — Lakecia Gunter</title>
<style>
  :root{--pink:#ff6b9d;--deep:#e8558a;--ink:#1a1a1a;--paper:#fafafa;--muted:#666666;--line:#e0e0e0}
  *{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0}
  body{background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink);font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,sans-serif;line-height:1.5;font-size:16px}
  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
  img{max-width:100%;display:block}
  
  .nav{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 32px;font-size:14px;position:relative;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--paper)}
  .brand{font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.01em}
  .nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px}
  .nav-links a{color:var(--muted);transition:color .2s}
  .nav-links a:hover{color:var(--ink)}
  .menu-toggle{display:block !important;background:none;border:none;font-size:28px;cursor:pointer;padding:8px}
  
  
    .menu-toggle{display:block}
    .nav-links{display:none;position:absolute;top:100%;left:0;right:0;background:var(--paper);padding:24px 32px;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;z-index:100;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
    .nav-links.active{display:flex}
  }
  
  .hero{padding:60px 32px;max-width:1200px;margin:auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:60px;align-items:center}
  .hero h1{font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,64px);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.03em;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:20px}
  .hero p{font-size:18px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:28px}
  .hero img{width:100%;height:480px;object-fit:cover;border-radius:4px}
  .button{display:inline-block;background:var(--ink);color:var(--paper);padding:14px 28px;font-size:14px;font-weight:500;cursor:pointer;border:none;border-radius:4px}
  .button:hover{background:var(--muted)}
  
  .timeline{padding:80px 32px;max-width:1200px;margin:auto}
  .timeline h2{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:48px;color:var(--muted)}
  .timeline-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:120px 1fr;gap:40px;padding:32px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}
  .timeline-item:first-child{padding-top:0}
  .timeline-year{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--deep);letter-spacing:.02em}
  .timeline-content h3{font-size:20px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}
  .timeline-content p{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}
  .timeline-content .org{font-size:14px;color:var(--deep);font-weight:600;margin-top:4px}
  
  .stats{padding:60px 32px;max-width:1200px;margin:auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:40px;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
  .stat h3{font-size:40px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.03em;margin-bottom:8px;color:var(--deep)}
  .stat p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5}
  
  .services{padding:80px 32px;max-width:1200px;margin:auto;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
  .services h2{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:48px;color:var(--muted)}
  .service-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:32px}
  .service-card{padding:32px;background:#fff;border-radius:4px;border:1px solid var(--line)}
  .service-card h3{font-size:20px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px}
  .service-card p{font-size:15px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}
  
  .cta-section{padding:80px 32px;text-align:center;background:var(--ink);color:var(--paper)}
  .cta-section h2{font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.03em;margin-bottom:16px}
  .cta-section p{font-size:18px;color:#999;margin-bottom:32px}
  .cta-section .button{background:var(--paper);color:var(--ink)}
  .cta-section .button:hover{background:var(--deep);color:var(--paper)}
  
  .footer{padding:32px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);max-width:1200px;margin:auto;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
  
  
    .hero{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px}
    .stats{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}
    .service-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .timeline-item{grid-template-columns:80px 1fr;gap:24px}
    .footer{flex-direction:column;gap:12px;text-align:center}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="nav">
  <a href="/shotgun-12/v7-cv/" class="brand">Lakecia Gunter</a>
  <button class="menu-toggle" onclick="document.querySelector('.nav-links').classList.toggle('active')">&#9776;</button>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/shotgun-12/v7-cv/">Home</a>
    <a href="/shotgun-12/v7-cv/about/">About</a>
    <a href="/shotgun-12/v7-cv/services/">Services</a>
    <a href="/shotgun-12/v7-cv/contact/">Contact</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div>
    <h1>Lakecia Gunter</h1>
    <p>Technology executive, board director, and advisor. Twenty-five years building and governing technology at enterprise scale. Now helping women leaders navigate AI with confidence and authority.</p>
    <a href="/shotgun-12/v7-cv/contact/" class="button">Schedule a consultation</a>
  </div>
  <div>
    <img src="../../lakecia.jpg" alt="Lakecia Gunter">
  </div>
</section>

<section class="timeline">
  <h2>Professional Timeline</h2>
  
  <div class="timeline-item">
    <div class="timeline-year">2023</div>
    <div class="timeline-content">
      <h3>Co-Founding Advisor</h3>
      <p>Helping companies navigate AI-driven technology change and strategic transformation.</p>
      <div class="org">TechArena.ai</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="timeline-item">
    <div class="timeline-year">2022</div>
    <div class="timeline-content">
      <h3>Independent Director</h3>
      <p>Strategic oversight and technology governance for publicly traded company.</p>
      <div class="org">IDEX Corporation (NYSE)</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="timeline-item">
    <div class="timeline-year">2021</div>
    <div class="timeline-content">
      <h3>Chief Technology Officer</h3>
      <p>Led $1B+ AI partner ecosystem and digital transformation initiatives.</p>
      <div class="org">Microsoft Global Partner Solutions</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="timeline-item">
    <div class="timeline-year">2018</div>
    <div class="timeline-content">
      <h3>Chief of Staff to CEO</h3>
      <p>Strategic advisor to CEO on technology and business priorities.</p>
      <div class="org">Intel Corporation</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="timeline-item">
    <div class="timeline-year">1999</div>
    <div class="timeline-content">
      <h3>Digital Logic Designer</h3>
      <p>Started career building technology for national security applications.</p>
      <div class="org">Department of Defense</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="stats">
  <div class="stat">
    <h3>25+</h3>
    <p>Years in technology leadership</p>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <h3>$1B+</h3>
    <p>Platform scale managed</p>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <h3>NYSE</h3>
    <p>Public company governance</p>
  </div>
  <div class="stat">
    <h3>50</h3>
    <p>Top Black Business Women US</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="services">
  <h2>Current Services</h2>
  <div class="service-grid">
    <div class="service-card">
      <h3>Board AI Fluency</h3>
      <p>Private sessions for boards and executive committees. Translate technical risk into governance language.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <h3>Executive Coaching</h3>
      <p>One-on-one partnership for women navigating AI adoption. Build confidence through judgment.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <h3>Implementation Sprints</h3>
      <p>Hands-on 2-4 week engagements. Move from strategy to execution with real tools.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <h3>Leadership Circle</h3>
      <p>Small cohort of women leaders navigating AI together. Monthly sessions, peer support.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <h2>Ready to lead with AI?</h2>
  <p>Book a free 30-minute strategy call. No pitch, just clarity.</p>
  <a href="/shotgun-12/v7-cv/contact/" class="button">Book your call</a>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <span>Lakecia Gunter — AI Strategy for Women Leaders</span>
  <span><a href="/shotgun-12/v7-cv/contact/">Contact</a></span>
</footer>

</body>
</html>